description:
🔊 Bristolian MLOps Community

📅 Save the date

Looking forward to our next Bristol Meetup!

This time we are hosting it in the amazing [Graphcore](https://www.graphcore.ai/) office!

Talk 1
\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-
**From MLOops to MLOps: LLMs & Stable Diffusion in the Cloud**
Alex Payot – AI Engineer at Graphcore

Alex’s talk will describe his team’s journey towards successfully making 30 models available in the cloud and will also include a short demo.

Talk 2
\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-
Laszlo Sragner \- Founder @ Hypergolic \| Startup Advisor \| Productionised Machine Learning \| Blog: laszlo\.substack\.com

As usual 🍻 and 🍕 and a trip to the pub afterward.

See you all soon!
title: MLOps Bristol - Meetup #8
